data.title: Camp Rock 2: The Final Jam
data.meta_description: Where to watch Camp Rock 2: The Final Jam (2010) starring Demi Lovato, Joe Jonas, Nick Jonas and directed by Paul Hoen.
data.text: Mitchie is back with her friends at Camp Rock, ready to perform music, dance and have a good time. Her "boyfriend" is there as well. A new camp has opened across the lake, creating an atmosphere of competition or feud.
